## Architecture (stage progression)

| Concept | Location | Notes |
|---------|----------|-------|
| Shape roster | `GAME_SHAPES` in `src/constants/game.ts` | 12 modes; index = `shapeIndex` |
| Pool tiers | `POOL_TIER_*` in `game.ts` | Core / Mid / Advanced / B |
| Active pool | `getActivePool(level)` | See table below |
| Stage count | `getStageCountForLevel(level)` | Target 5 / 7 / 8–10; capped by pool size |
| Level shuffle | `sampleStageOrder(pool, count)` | Random subset + Fisher-Yates order |
| New level | `createNewLevelState(level)` | Fresh pool sample + `stageSlot = 0` |
| Runtime state | `stageOrder`, `stageSlot` | `shapeIndex = stageOrder[stageSlot]` |
| Save / resume | `ISavedGame` incl. mode-specific fields | `jellyCells`, `stoneCells`, etc. |
| Stars | `stars_L${level}_S${shapeIndex}` | Keyed by shape, not slot |

**Helpers:** `shuffleIndices`, `getActivePool`, `getStageCountForLevel`, `sampleStageOrder`, `pickRandomCellPositions`, `createNewLevelState`, `resolveStageFromSave`, `computeGoalAfterSteps`

**Files:** `src/constants/game.ts`, `src/hooks/useCandyBreak.ts`

### Pool tiers (`GAME_SHAPES` indices)

| Tier | Constant | Styles | Indices |
|------|----------|--------|---------|
| Core | `POOL_TIER_CORE` | `classic`, `color-target`, `locked-tiles`, `bomb-storm` | 0, 1, 2, 4 |
| Mid | `POOL_TIER_MID` | `timer-attack`, `move-saver`, `pure-match` | 5, 8, 9 |
| Advanced | `POOL_TIER_ADVANCED` | `multiplier-rush`, `order-collect`, `combo-goal` | 3, 6, 7 |
| B | `POOL_TIER_B` | `jelly-tiles`, `stone-blocks` | 10, 11 |

### Active pool by level

| Level | Pool |
|-------|------|
| 1–2 | Core |
| 3 | Core + Mid |
| 4 | Core + Mid + Tier B |
| 5 | Core + Mid + Advanced + Tier B |

### Stages per level

| Level | Target stages | Actual (current roster) |
|-------|---------------|-------------------------|
| 1–2 | 5 | **4** (core pool size) |
| 3–4 | 5 / 7 | min(target, pool size) |
| 5 | 8–10 | 8–10 |

