## Shipped fixes

### Tier B modes (step 7)

**`jelly-tiles`** (index 10)
- ~15% of cells have jelly overlay (`JELLY_TILES_RATIO`)
- Goal: clear all jelly — removed when that cell is part of a match
- Candy swaps normally; green border overlay in UI

**`stone-blocks`** (index 11)
- ~12% of cells are stones (`STONE_BLOCKS_RATIO`); 1 adjacent match breaks each
- Goal: destroy all stones; blocks selection like frozen tiles
- Gray 🪨 overlay UI

Only appear in pools for **level 4+** (`getActivePool`).

