### Basket fall-in + goal bar (step 9)

Replaces the old in-cell blink (scale/rotate/fade) with Candy Crush–style collection into a slim goal bar below the grid.

**Match animation (`FlyingCandy`)**
- Matched candies render in an absolute overlay above the grid (`flyingCandyLayer`); in-grid candy + special overlay hidden while flying
- Motion: pop (scale ~1.32×) → gravity fall with delayed horizontal convergence toward bar center → tumble → fade at landing
- Target: `basketCollectX/Y` = center of bar below grid
- Bar squashes on landing (`basketBounce` / `basketSquishY`)
- `MATCH_ANIMATION_MS` = **500** in `App.tsx` and `useCandyBreak.ts` (must stay in sync — hook clears matched cells mid-cascade on this timer)

**Goal bar UI (`CollectionBasket`)**
- Full-width pill bar only (~28px: `BASKET_BAR_HEIGHT` 20 + frame 4×2); no mouth hole, no label text
- Gold frame, dark track, animated fill width driven by `goalFillRatio` (`goalProgress / goal`); fill **color** is per-stage mixed candy hue (not fixed gold)
- **Per-stage fill hue:** `getStageBarFillColor(level, shapeIndex, stageSlot)` — weighted blend of two candy hex colors from curated pairs (Red+Blue excluded to avoid muddy purple); blend ratio 0.28–0.72; stable per stage, changes on advance
- Candy hex palette: Red `#FF5A5F`, Blue `#4D96FF`, Gold `#FFD93D`, Mint `#6BCB77`

**Layout**
- `cellSize` uses **original** height formula (no basket reserve) — playboard not shrunk for the slim bar
- Bar + gap sit in `boardWrapper` bottom padding: `max(ANDROID_BOTTOM_SAFE_INSET, BASKET_GAP + BASKET_TOTAL + 4)`
- `ANDROID_BOTTOM_SAFE_INSET` = 64px on Android (gesture nav, e.g. Galaxy S25); `IOS_BOTTOM_EXTRA_INSET` = 8px

**Hook exports added:** `shapeIndex`, `stageSlot` (for bar color seed + future UI)

**Files:** `App.tsx`, `src/hooks/useCandyBreak.ts`

**Evolution (this session):** big wooden tray + emoji → slim bar with progress → restore grid size → per-stage mixed fill colors


## Play styles (current — 12 modes)

| Idx | Style | Goal | Pool | Notes |
|-----|-------|------|------|-------|
| 0 | `classic` | Clear N candies | Core | Bomb at 60% moves |
| 1 | `color-target` | Clear N of target color | Core | Random target |
| 2 | `locked-tiles` | Thaw all frozen | Core | 2 adjacent hits |
| 3 | `multiplier-rush` | Score threshold | Advanced | Combo multiplier max 8× |
| 4 | `bomb-storm` | Clear N candies | Core | Bomb respawns |
| 5 | `timer-attack` | Clear N candies | Mid | 90s countdown |
| 6 | `order-collect` | Colors in sequence | Advanced | Red/Blue/Gold queue |
| 7 | `combo-goal` | N cascade steps | Advanced | Step 2+ only |
| 8 | `move-saver` | Clear N candies | Mid | Cascade refunds moves |
| 9 | `pure-match` | Clear N candies | Mid | No specials |
| 10 | `jelly-tiles` | Clear all jelly | **Tier B** | Match on jelly cell |
| 11 | `stone-blocks` | Break all stones | **Tier B** | 1 adjacent hit |

